This topic contains the release notes for VMware Spring Cloud® Data Flow for Kubernetes version 1.2.

## <a id="1-2-1"></a>v1.2.1

**Release Date: February 9, 2021**

### <a id='features'></a> Features

Features included in this release:

- Spring Cloud Data Flow has been updated to SCDF Pro version 1.1.2
- Spring Cloud Skipper has been updated to 2.6.1
- Composed Task Runner 2.7.1 container image is now provided

